subject: Add a fsck symlink to btrfsck
commitMessage:
Add a fsck symlink to btrfsck

In order for fsck to work for btrfs, the 'fsck.btrfs' binary must exist.

This commit creates a symlink with this name, pointing to the packaged
fsck tool.

Change-Id: Id512747404e2b9862451b9df7f8c3febc68db03b
